ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
SubjectOrder Amending Part 1 of the Schedule to the Act
PrecisOrder Amending Part 1 of the Schedule to the Royal Canadian Mint Act in order to add to it the denominations of $1,250 and $1,000 to allow the Mint to issue and produce numismatic coins with these denominations in the future.
